                            <comment id="466473" author="yujian" created="Wed, 6 Aug 2025 18:43:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I just found increasing the value of &lt;tt&gt;LDD_PARAM_LEN&lt;/tt&gt; could make &lt;tt&gt;tunefs.lustre&lt;/tt&gt; pass with long params, however, &lt;tt&gt;mount.lustre&lt;/tt&gt; would fail as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;error: add mount options param=...... too long, 6376 over limit 4096
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The error was from &lt;tt&gt;append_option()&lt;/tt&gt; in &lt;tt&gt;lustre/utils/mount_lustre.c&lt;/tt&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;append_option()&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
out_err:
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/* &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;too &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt; message is checked in conf-sanity test_98 */&lt;/span&gt;
        fprintf(stderr,
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;error: add mount options %s%s too &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt;, %zu over limit %zu\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,
                param, value, strlen(options) + strlen(param) + strlen(value),
                options_len);
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; E2BIG;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And the &lt;tt&gt;options_len&lt;/tt&gt; was defined as &lt;tt&gt;maxopt_len&lt;/tt&gt; in &lt;tt&gt;main()&lt;/tt&gt; as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
        size_t maxopt_len;
        size_t g_pagesize;

        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// ......
&lt;/span&gt;        g_pagesize = sysconf(_SC_PAGESIZE);
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// ......
&lt;/span&gt;        maxopt_len = MIN(g_pagesize, 64 * 1024);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So, the limitation is  4096.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="466409" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 6 Aug 2025 14:23:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Doesn&apos;t this change break compatibility? I need to look at the libmount API for handling this.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
